WEBVTT

00:00:54.062 --> 00:01:00.112
we faced the tremendous challenges
of a post-conflict nation:

00:01:01.366 --> 00:01:03.097
collapsed economy,

00:01:04.907 --> 00:01:06.788
destroyed infrastructure,

00:01:08.129 --> 00:01:10.724
dysfunctional institutions,

00:01:11.680 --> 00:01:13.193
enormous debt,

00:01:14.603 --> 00:01:16.888
bloated civil service.

00:01:18.140 --> 00:01:19.570
We also faced

00:01:21.634 --> 00:01:26.094
the challenges of those left behind.

